lk:prev;\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-primary flex-none\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"m3.87 7.996 6.626-6.626 1.626 1.626-5 5 5 5-1.626 1.627z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"border-dirty-seagull bg-main-level-1 lg:bg-main-level-1/75 hover:bg-main-level-1 text-slide-arrow absolute top-1/2 flex h-10 w-10 -translate-y-1/2 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-full border right-[8px] lg:right-[24px]\" data-testid=\"next-button\" data-ylk=\"ct:slideshow;elm:arrow;itc:1;sec:sshow;slk:next;\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-primary flex-none\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12.128 8.001 5.5 14.628 3.875 13l5-5-5-5 1.626-1.626z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"absolute top-[8px] right-[8px] rounded bg-black/40 px-1 py-0.5 text-sm text-white lg:top-[12px] lg:right-[12px] lg:px-2 lg:py-1\"><span class=\"font-bold\" data-testid=\"current-index\">1</span><span data-testid=\"total-index\"> / <!-- -->2</span></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-px16 mb-1 leading-[1.35] font-bold lg:mb-2\">俄烏停火期望推動歐洲股市上漲 諾和諾德股價反彈</h2></div></div></div>",
